        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        <p><strong>"claude: command not found"</strong> — Node.js global bin isn't in your PATH. Try <span class="ic">npx @anthropic-ai/claude-code</span>, or reinstall Node.js from nodejs.org.</p>
        <p><strong>"Invalid API key"</strong> — The key may have been copied incorrectly. Go to console.anthropic.com and create a new one.</p>
        <p><strong>"Rate limit exceeded"</strong> — You've hit the API rate limit. Wait a minute and try again.</p>
        <p><strong>Skills not working</strong> — Verify that <span class="ic">~/.claude/skills/code-review/SKILL.md</span> exists. If not, run <span class="ic">install.sh</span> again.</p>

